    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptionally well-kept mint-condition car that presents beautifully throughout. The paint, trim, and interior all show extremely light wear at most, and the overall finish is the kind that stands out immediately in person. It appears complete, highly cared for, and ready for a buyer who wants a top-quality example rather than a project or rough driver. Expect a very clean, well-preserved car with excellent visual appeal and only the slightest signs of normal use.",
