    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition car that shows well overall and appears to have been cared for properly. The exterior presents nicely with the kind of minor cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle, and the interior looks tidy and complete rather than overly worn. It should be a solid, enjoyable driver for someone looking for a well-kept example, but buyers should still expect normal age- and use-related imperfections rather than a showpiece.",
