    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Opportunity-priced and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers affordable entry into ownership for the right buyer. It shows clear cosmetic and mechanical wear consistent with its condition, but it still presents as a practical project, parts donor, or budget transportation candidate. If you\u2019re looking for a low-cost vehicle with potential and prefer straightforward value over flash, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
