      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runaround that could suit someone handy or anyone after an affordable project. It\u2019s a great opportunity to get into a car without spending a fortune, and with a bit of TLC it could still have plenty to give. Priced to sell and ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with strong mechanical character and plenty of usable life left. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission does its job, and the chassis still feels composed enough to enjoy on the road. It shows cosmetic wear and age-related needs, but it presents as an honest, serviceable car that could be driven as-is while being improved over time. Great candidate for someone who wants affordable entry into ownership with real upside.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest beater with plenty of life for the right buyer. Cheap way into a car now. Priced to move.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
